title: [Ondreian's Magic Shoppe]
[Ondreian's General Store]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A floral-etched ceramic case sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the wooden floor.

A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and an uneven wooden ceiling rises overhead.  A worn rug sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is a floral-etched ceramic case on one side of the shop.
